cs.MA, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.RO 

This paper deals with a problem of maintaining connectivity in a multiagent surveillance network, which involves communication and coordination among multiple agents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The paper also discusses the use of communication networks, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The proposed strategy is decentralized, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also deals with maintaining situational awareness, which could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses the use of agents, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics).
